author: Alisha Buaya For Daily Mail Australia
title: Actor Chris Hemsworth flaunts his muscular biceps
text:
He's currently filming the next installment of The Avengers franchise.
And Australian actor Chris Hemsworth is seen flaunting his massive biceps in a video uploaded by a fan, who was in an elevator with the Thor star.
In the clip, the 33-year-old star appears to have finished up a session at the gym, sporting a tight fitting white singlet and headphones around his neck.
Impressed? Australian actor Chris Hemsworth is seen flaunting his massive biceps in a video uploaded by a fan, who was in an elevator with the Thor star
He takes to the very back of the lift, and looks suspiciously at the camera while his large arms are folded.
The father-of-three notices the man taking a selfie with the phone and quickly strikes a pose.
Chris' flashes his big cheeky grin and flaunts his bulging biceps in the candid footage.
Bulging biceps: He enters the lift looking suspiciously at the fan taking a selfie and quickly strikes a pose
Give the fans the gun show: Chris' flashes his big cheeky grin and flexes his arm, making each muscle and vein visibly pronounced
As he flexes his arm, individual muscles become visible and veins more pronounced.
His buff physique is a testament to his workout regime and diet for his role as the hammer-wielding, Norse god of thunder.
With his arms taking central focus, it almost takes up at least half the frame.
Loved up: Chris and his wife Spanish actress Elsa Pataky have been in Los Angeles for the past few weeks attending the award shows
One of Hollywood's busiest: Chris is currently shooting the next Avengers film and military film Horse Soldiers
Chris has been in Los Angeles for the past few weeks for awards season, accompanied by wife Spanish actress Elsa Pataky.
The Home And Away alum is busy shooting the next Avengers film and military film Horse Soldiers.
Together the couple have their three children India Rose, 4, twins Tristan and Sasha, 2.
